Ranger Help for: animal lure
=============================

SYNTAX:      lure <race>
USAGE:       Wilderness
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     40
SKILL TYPE:  husbandry

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to lure a temporary wild animal to their
location by mimicking its calls and scent. The lured animal will fight
alongside the Ranger for a limited time before wandering off. The type
of animal that can be lured depends on the terrain. Unlike a bonded
follower, a lured animal is not permanent and cannot be trained. This
skill is useful when the Ranger needs temporary combat assistance.
